##Record Wuhan epidemic under the First Line of Defense: More than 300"infrared guard" guarding the city

Micro signal

Function introduction, the official account of tecent science and technology of tecent news banner, read technology here!

Affected by the epidemic, the demand for non-contact infrared thermometers is continuing to increase, and orders for related enterprises are also growing rapidly. At present, the infrared equipment enterprises represented by gaode infrared, Dali Technology, Jiuzhiyang, Kangtuo infrared have actively deployed production capacity, overtime to ensure the production and supply of products.

Source: Periscope

By Guo Xiaofeng

The XT236, a seemingly ordinary string of characters, is the first line of Defense in Wuhan, the city with the worst case of COVID-19 pneumonia.

Workers install the XT236, a fully automatic infrared temperature screening device, at the Zhongshan Park Station at the Line 2, Wuhan Metro on Feb. 3,2010.

"Today's task is to install one at Gate B at Zhongshan Station, two at Exit C, three at Exit B at Hanzheng Street station, and four at Dazhi Road Station V and D. At present Wuhan subway has installed about 30 sets, basically achieved full coverage."Gao de Infrared after-sales Service Department manager Shu Jun told"periscope".

The day before, Wuhan Huoshenshan Hospital completed delivery, Raytheon Hospital delivery is imminent, XT236 is also the first time installed in these two hospitals and hotels for doctors accommodation. XT236 as the first line of Defense for temperature monitoring, it is used to protect the medical staff and logistics support staff to monitor the body temperature in real time, effectively avoid cross-infection.

The main task of the army is scheduling, that is, where the installation of equipment to arrange the first-line workers to install, followed by the provision of after-sales technical services. Currently, including Wuhan Tianhe Airport, Wuhan high-speed Railway Station, Wuhan Railway Station, Wuhan Union Hospital and other personnel-intensive areas have been deployed XT236. According to Shu Jun, from the outbreak so far, the German infrared in Wuhan installed nearly 300 sets of infrared temperature rapid screening instrument, more than 500 sets of the province. "The overall number is still growing. "

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
In the face of the Spring Festival travel rush, prevention and control has become a top priority, especially for the temperature detection. So far, nearly 2,000 sets of automatic infrared body temperature screening machines made by gaode have been installed in hospitals, stations, airports and other crowded public places in Beijing, Shanghai, Guangdong, Fujian, Zhejiang, Jiangsu, Sichuan, Yunnan and Anhui.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
A single image can measure up to 100 body temperatures

According to the Bundle Jun, from the end of December last year, the German infrared has started on some places on the installation of equipment. "We are a professional and technical enterprise with the ability to prevent and control the epidemic, so we are more alert, and we started to be prepared when we first saw the news of coronavirus pneumonia. "

17 years ago, under the background that China's capability of prevention and control of SARS was not mature enough, the first generation of infrared human temperature measuring equipment was developed. "This is now Josiah Goddard's fourth generation of infrared temperature measurement products, after many rounds of iteration, the latest equipment can realize face detection, no contact can be achieved to collect passenger temperature, beyond a certain range to issue an intercept alert, no fever symptoms of passengers quickly through the basic sense, " said Wang Peng, head of infrared products technology in Germany, said.

According to Shu Jun, before the outbreak was announced on January 14, the installed capacity was about a few units per day, and on the 14th the installation capacity began to increase. "nearly 50 units were installed that day, and the workers worked for two days without a break, and now the maximum is hundreds a day. " For him and his front-line installers, one more device means more people can not be infected.

Body temperature measurement equipment is mainly divided into contact and non-contact, the biggest difference between the two is whether to contact the skin of the tested, the current epidemic prevention and control are mostly non-contact thermometer, XT236 belongs to the latter. It is called the first defense line of epidemic prevention and control because of three characteristics: "non-contact temperature measurement" , "large-scale crowd real-time temperature measurement" , "automatic capture fever crowd" .

As an infectious disease, the most difficult point of prevention and treatment of NCP lies in its high infectivity in close contact. Traditional thermometers, such as Mercury-in-glass thermometer, frontal thermometers, and point thermometers, require direct or close contact with the person being tested, which poses a significant risk of cross infection.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
The rapid infrared temperature screening device can solve this problem, it not only does not need to have direct contact with the person being tested, but also can keep the detection distance under the condition of not affecting the detection results.

XT236, for example, has a maximum temperature measuring distance of 10 meters, which greatly reduces the exposure risk of testing personnel.

After solving the difficulty of temperature measurement contact, it is necessary to ensure the timeliness of temperature measurement. People-intensive places such as trains, planes and long-distance bus stations are the key points for preventing and controlling the Spring Festival travel rush.

The detection of infrared radiation of human body is carried out in real time by the infrared body temperature rapid screening instrument. The temperature data obtained by the Algorithm is in milliseconds. When the system is working, it does not need the crowd to make any stay at all, once a person enters the monitoring area of the device, temperature data can be taken immediately. Another advantage of thermal imaging is the ability to capture temperature distribution images, that is, to get a picture of all the temperature data, so that even large groups of people entering the system at the same time, you can also take everyone's temperature at once.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
According to Shu Jun, as long as the personnel into the Lens have imaging, picture can show its temperature. "usually we screen out the person on the furthest and nearest edge of the frame until he's in range, in order to improve accuracy. Currently the same video interface can detect more than 50 people, many times hundreds of people, depending on the location and density of people in the Lens. One-day measurements vary depending on the location, and it's not unusual for airports to have more than 100,000 or even a million locations."

Infrared equipment installation location is not random, indoor, constant temperature, ventilation, angle is the key to ensure accurate temperature measurement. With Colonel Winn, it's been a long process. "In order to measure temperature more accurately, we need to proofread the temperature according to the range of human body temperature, and put the corresponding data and curves into the equipment. The final precision of temperature measurement of the equipment is as high as 0.3 C, which is very high in the world, " said Shu.

Because the airport and train stations are so crowded with people, if you just measure everyone's temperature, then the staff will still have a lot of work to do, even if you have to stare at the computer screen 24 hours a day, otherwise at any time may have a fever personnel miss, and cause a bigger problem. In view of this application scenario, XT236 has specially designed "automatic alarm capture" function.

The system can set an alarm temperature, such as 37.3 C. when the body temperature of many people is monitored in real time, the system will automatically compare the obtained temperature with the alarm temperature. Once the temperature is higher than 37.3 C, the system will automatically alarm, at the same time, the infrared temperature image and the visible light image of the heating personnel are automatically recorded for the inspection and confirmation of the staff. At the same time XT236 also through advanced Ai Algorithm, with face recognition function, only to measure the face temperature, while automatically tracking and capturing a number of heating people.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
Large capacity GAP, 5G power

"In the past, infrared temperature measuring equipment was mainly used in airports, ports and other places of entry and exit. The production and installation were not large. Last year, only a few hundred units were shipped. At present, we are delivering about 300 sets of products nationwide every day, which is the total for the past year or even two years,"Shu told periscope. As we all know, before infrared equipment used for military products, less civilian.

In 2003 SARS epidemic situation, the first generation infrared human body temperature measuring equipment developed by Gaode infrared was put into use and played a key role. In 2013, the infrared thermal imaging industrial base was put into operation, and the localization of the detectors was realized, breaking the technical blockade of foreign countries. At present, gaode infrared industrial park has been built to cover the bottom of the infrared core devices to the top of the integrated optoelectronic system of the whole industry chain development base.

Because Josiah Goddard's infrared temperature rapid screening system uses all its own infrared detectors with its own intellectual property rights, and because the core devices are not subject to human control, make High German infrared can be in the outbreak of the initial production, supply is relatively adequate.

It is understood that Josiah Goddard is also continuing to develop and upgrade other products, plans to launch 3-4 models to deal with the epidemic prevention and control, and added 15,000 sets of production plans, which will be produced at a rate of 1,000 sets per day, to provide more products in a short time to support the epidemic prevention and control work throughout the country. In addition to the rapid screening of infrared thermometers for large populations, Josiah Goddard's handheld infrared thermometers are also being expanded.

Another infrared company, Zhejiang Dali Technology, also said that as of February 2, Dali Technology had more than 1,000 sets of equipment deployed to the epidemic areas of Wuhan and Hubei, beijing, Shanghai, Zhejiang, Jiangsu, Guangdong and nearly 20 provinces and municipalities and Hong Kong, Macao and Taiwan regions, airport hubs, railway stations, customs ports, hospitals and office buildings and other densely populated places. Dali Technology also stressed that the company's current production capacity is sufficient, according to the epidemic prevention and control needs to further increase capacity.

According to the latest research report released by Galaxy Securities, according to the latest information on the Ministry of Industry and Information Technology website on February 2, the Ministry of Industry and Information Technology has received a total of about 20,000 sets of infrared body temperature detectors from various places, with more than 300,000 sets of hand-held models, these figures are preliminary estimates. According to the situation of epidemic prevention and control, the Ministry of Industry and Information Technology estimates that the market demand for full-automatic infrared temperature detector is about 60,000 units, handheld about 550,000 units. Judging from the current market capacity, the gap is larger.

Lu Jing, chairman of Hangzhou Malleck Technology Co. , Ltd. , said in an interview with China Electronics Daily that as of January 31, hangzhou malleck infrared temperature sensor has been sent to 400,000 sets of customers for the production of infrared thermometer. "Even though we are working round the clock, we still can not fully meet the needs of our customers. The gap is still large and the company is arranging more employees to assist with overtime production, " Lu said.

A person in the industry told periscope that the low rate of returning to work during the Spring Festival, coupled with the limited logistics affected by the epidemic, are the main factors that have led to the inability to keep up with production capacity, but this should be temporary. With the resumption of work after the festival, the gap in market demand is expected to gradually fill. Currently, similar to CHONGDA technology as infrared body temperature testing and related medical equipment core components suppliers, with the support of the relevant departments, part of the current production line has been resumed.

It is worth mentioning that the combination of infrared equipment and 5G in the fight against this epidemic has also caused concern.

On February 2, Guangdong Mobile introduced "5G + infrared" temperature measurement information application, and the biggest difference from the traditional infrared equipment above is that it is more flexible. Lin Xiao, Guangdong Mobile Information Integration Center, said in an interview with periscope that the 5G infrared test system can meet the needs of large data volume and high mobility scenarios. On the one hand, the traditional infrared temperature measurement equipment through the network cable to achieve data transmission, limited the application of equipment scene. The appearance of 5G technology satisfies this demand well, the system can adjust the position at any time according to the use demand, the crowd situation and so on factors. On the other hand, the infrared temperature measurement system can be connected with the video monitoring platform through 5G technology. First, it can be combined with the face recognition function of the back end to effectively realize the source tracing of the personnel after the temperature measurement. Second, it can realize the centralized monitoring of the temperature measurement, improve work efficiency.

It is understood that Guangdong Province has already deployed more than 200 sets of equipment in an emergency. At present, they have already been deployed to Guangzhou Wanda Plaza, Shantou Jinping District People's Hospital, Wujiang District Government of the People's Republic of China and other key projects. It is expected that more than 1,000 sets of equipment will be deployed throughout the province. "More than 100 units have put forward to Guangdong mobile the use of "5G + infrared" temperature applications demand, " said Lin.

In the face of the epidemic situation, infrared temperature built up the first line of defense. They are like a pair of heat detection eyes, can quickly find and track the higher body temperature of the people, in tension and running to protect the safety of the people throughout the country.
